        "text": "Suppose now that |n/5k J = 4. Then we must also have 20 ≤ \\n/5k-'J ≤ 24. The former condition implies that the last term of the above sum is 1/5k = 1/(12.5k-3), which has 5-valuation - (k - 2).",
